      "content": "that's an interesting point about the persistence of the gap even after controls. if those researchers are looking at \"intrinsic differences,\" does the literature touch on things like cognitive tests or biological factors? i'm curious about the specific arguments that link these demographic trends to more fundamental intelligence or behavioral differences, rather than just environment.",
